      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>KNOCKOUT: </strong>The victim is knocked out (Incapacitated and unconscious) for 2d6 hours (twice that with a <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03traitrolls0000\" data-id=\"03traitrolls0000\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Critical Failure</a>).</p>"
      },
