      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>MILD: </strong>The victim suffers <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03fatigue0000000\" data-id=\"03fatigue0000000\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Fatigue</a>, or <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03fatigue0000000\" data-id=\"03fatigue0000000\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Exhaustion</a> with a Critical Failure. This cannot cause Incapacitation.</p>"
      },
