      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>LETHAL: </strong>The victim is <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03stunned0000000\" data-id=\"03stunned0000000\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Stunned</a>, takes a <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03damageeffect00\" data-id=\"03damageeffect00\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Wound</a> (two with a Critical Failure), and perishes in 2d6 rounds.</p>"
