        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>DEBILITATING: </strong>The victim becomes <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03distractedan00\" data-id=\"03distractedan00\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Distracted</a> for 5 rounds (twice that with a <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03traitrolls0000\" data-id=\"03traitrolls0000\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Critical Failure</a>).</p>"
