    {
      "sort": 50000,
      "name": "Damaging",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "NFvly6GX075uoh2x",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><strong>DAMAGING: </strong>The victim must make a Vigor roll as a free action at the beginning of their next turn. Failure causes one <a class=\"content-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-link data-uuid=\"Compendium.swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JournalEntry.swadecor03rules0.JournalEntryPage.03damageeffect00\" data-id=\"03damageeffect00\" data-type=\"JournalEntryPage\" data-pack=\"swade-core-rules.swade-rules\" data-tooltip=\"Text Page\">Wound</a> and the victim must make another Vigor roll next turn. Success means the victim doesn't suffer a Wound, but must make a Vigor roll again next turn. A raise recovers from the poison and no further rolls are required.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
